This is entry format for the POST method

open postman
create new http request
in the search bar type-> http://127.0.0.1:5000/add_location
click n body then -> raw then -> select JSON file
now in that blank space copy paste the above format and click on send
once it updates u can change the data in the format and click send to contine updating